<section class="lp-section" id="faq">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5 lp-reveal">
            <span class="lp-section-badge">FAQ</span>
            <h2 class="lp-section-title mt-2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p class="lp-section-sub">Got questions? We have answers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="accordion lp-accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item lp-faq-item lp-reveal lp-delay-1">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button lp-faq-btn" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                                What type of businesses can use ZoneBill?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body lp-faq-body">
                                ZoneBill is built for time-based entertainment venues — billiard halls, board game cafés, KTV bars, escape rooms, gaming shops, and hybrid café-entertainment setups. If you bill by the hour and manage tables or rooms, ZoneBill fits.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item lp-faq-item lp-reveal lp-delay-2">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button lp-faq-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                                How does the QR customer portal work?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body lp-faq-body">
                                Each table or room gets a unique QR code. Your customers scan it to view their running bill, elapsed time, and any food/drink orders placed — completely in real time. No app download required.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item lp-faq-item lp-reveal lp-delay-3">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button lp-faq-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                                Do I need accounting knowledge to use the accounting features?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body lp-faq-body">
                                No. ZoneBill auto-posts journal entries for every POS invoice, so the books stay accurate by default. You can review chart of accounts and export reports for your accountant — no manual entry needed.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item lp-faq-item lp-reveal lp-delay-4">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button lp-faq-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                                Can I manage multiple staff roles?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body lp-faq-body">
                                Yes. ZoneBill supports three staff roles: Main Admin, Manager, and Cashier. Each role has tailored access — cashiers operate the POS, managers see reports and manage inventory, and admins control everything including billing and user management.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item lp-faq-item lp-reveal lp-delay-5">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button lp-faq-btn collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                                Is there a free trial?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body lp-faq-body">
                                Yes — every new business gets a 14-day free trial on any plan. No credit card required to start. You can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel at any time from your billing dashboard.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

